column5: Although most of us think you look just fine, The essence of middle aged manlyness, These may help you to "look" your best for that little cheerleader you used to date...wayyyy back when  http://www.ehow.com/how_4471656_look-thinner-week.html http://www.cellulitecuretips.com/look-thinner-in-a-week/ http://beauty.about.com/od/hairstylephotogalleries/qt/photopose.htm  Just remember, the youngsters you used to skip school with, and smoke in the bathroom with, and peek into the girls shower with are all about the same age you are, so, just be your rugged, outdoorsy self, and enjoy the memories dude!!!  Paul
Yah... but they all looked so much different, at Sturgeon Falls Public School, with a smoke in their hand in grade 1 Paul!
I didn't smoke till grade 3. AND I've been on the organizing committee for this so Saturdays the night.. i think if i drink enough, ill look slimmer.. to me anyway..

Ouch !!!!!!!!  One week after Lakeair !?? You better get to work on it right away !! You could always wrap elastic bandages around it . Just paint a belly button on it and glue on a bit of hair, and no one will know.
Thats Lakair,an ,TJ CAN OUT DRINK,OUT EAT ,AND OUT SLEEP,OOPS, got that backwards.
Hey you guys...watch it. That's TJ and he ain't heavy, he's my brudder.

Hey!! LOL.. were expecting 2-400 people, and I ain't cooking fish, lol.. but cause I'm on the organizing committee.. the only whisky we are serving is CROWN!!!! Then on Sunday, (OMG) its a drive up to up to Cochrane to flyin to Kesagami for 4 nights. Sumpting tells me is gonna be my ole lady drivin' and ill be a sleepin' lol.. thank Brian... a man has to know when to go down for the count.
